      <TR>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'
 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>Drexyll</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> It all depends on the lvl range.  Frankly, I felt gimp as hell in PVP until I got SOP at 24. I could generally get away, but I couldn't KILL very well. At 24+ I was able to compete, and quite well.  Not ONLY from that spell, but with it in addition to what I already had, the gap with other classes was closed.  Things were pretty smooth until late 30's or so, at which time, if a wizard jumped me, I ran like hell.  VOS is great at 34, but wizards are just too powerful at that lvl.  You'll never have time to lifetap back the dmg you take. But if nothing else, even in PVP we are excellent at escape : ).  </P><P>Things honestly don't pick up again until 51/54.  At 51 you get Ebolt/Splurt.  Ebolt seems to be resisted a lot less with the new resist changes, and honestly most ppl have crap PR anyway.  Splurt takes too long to do dmg unless you can keep them too busy to dispell it, which comes at 54.  Dinging 54 I felt Godly again.  Once you have deflux you can go toe to toe with any wizard (provided you have enough resist gear to get a partial or two in) or non-epic mage.  </P><P>Nowadays, if I get the "opening cast", I'm generally going to win.  Ebolt/Splurt and start defuxing away.  If I DONT get the opening cast, I still have a damn good chance vs a nuker.  Generally you're going to get 2 deflux's off for every 1 nuke you get hit with.  That's pretty powerful.  Most people don't even bother trying to kill a high lvl necro.</P><P>There are certain lvl's where any given class will be the best.  At one time, a lvl 9 (or maybe it was 6, I forget) cleric could outnuke a mage, for example.  Anyone that says necros are no good in PVP is either in one of our "bad spots" lvl-wise, or doesn't know how to PVP as a necro.  I'm actually planning on making ANOTHER necro, and lvling him to 27 or so and keeping him at that lvl just to PK with.</P><P></P><P><img src="http://www.onethirtyeight.com/graphics-2/cg.gif"></font></td>
